{"about_the_game":"<img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2429240/extras/soulslinger_envoy_of_death_long_description_death_is_calling_EN_620width_JUNE2023.png?t=1729677152\" /><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2429240/extras/souslinger_fighting_620x349_JULY2023.gif?t=1729677152\" /><br><br>Become an Envoy of Death, able to unleash the incredible powers that will make you the most dangerous soul in Limbo. Upgrade your character\u2019s abilities to become the ultimate Soulslinger and take on thrilling challenges in a bloody war against the criminal cartel of the afterlife!<br><br> <br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2429240/extras/soulslinger_envoy_of_death_long_description_meet_stray_souls_EN_620width_JUNE2023.png?t=1729677152\" /><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2429240/extras/souslinger_allies_enemies_620x349_JULY2023.gif?t=1729677152\" /><br><br>Step into the rich and immersive world of Haven, filled with mysterious NPCs who hold the secrets to its dark history. Be wary of the allies and enemies you make as every encounter might shape your journey ahead. In this mesmerizing western-fantasy world, you will experience a tale of grief, loss, and one man's obsession with cheating death itself.<br><br> <br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2429240/extras/soulslinger_envoy_of_death_long_description_craft_your_weapons_EN_620width_JUNE2023.png?t=1729677152\" /><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2429240/extras/souslinger_workshop_shotgun_fight_620x349_JULY2023.gif?t=1729677152\" /><br><br>Forge your own destiny with every run by crafting powerful weapons and unlocking permanent upgrades in Haven. Grow stronger with every new challenge and become an incredibly deadly gunslinger. Get ready for a fast-paced rogue-lite FPS experience you won\u2019t ever forget!<br><br> <br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2429240/extras/soulslinger_envoy_of_death_long_description_features_EN_620width_JUNE2023.png?t=1729677152\" /><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Fast-paced, story-driven roguelike FPS set in random sequences of rooms built in a unique western-fantasy world<br></li><li>Customize Soulslinger through a deep upgrade system<br></li><li>Experience a tightly written story filled with loyal allies and charismatic villains. The story adapts to what you do in the roguelike gameplay<br></li><li>Tons of gun fodder creeps that attack in waves, spiced up by challenging elite mobs</li></ul>","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Risk and reward","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2429240/7a6cdfb2077900ce565224e4effbf947835629be.jpg"},{"name":"Open with a bang","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2429240/17f65166841e2eeb253117b793c454c8d166238c.jpg"},{"name":"18th time's the charm","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2429240/ab6bbe0c846e6ca17d6b7e24bb659514b263ab7f.jpg"},{"name":"Poison them all!","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2429240/f8bd8f24cbf94d505929388b4ec7f3f70c26f674.jpg"},{"name":"Reloadslinger","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2429240/7f97eb8d53318ca95e9da9c0a6afb875a438e7fc.jpg"},{"name":"A hardened soul","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2429240/711525d638dfb1cf7e05c4d0ee578f0be2bebb84.jpg"},{"name":"Who needs powers","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2429240/092b2709f1a092a25c36d30d85200c86f2a